question: List all buffets and coffee shops open from 7:30am to 4:00pm.
sql_query1:
SELECT Restaurant.name 
FROM Restaurant
WHERE (Restaurant.Service_format = "Buffet" OR Restaurant.Service_format = "Coffee Shop") AND Restaurant.Hours = "7.30 a.m. - 4 p.m."
sql_query2:
SELECT Restaurant.name 
FROM Restaurant
WHERE Restaurant.Service_format = "Buffet" OR Restaurant.Service_format = "Coffee Shop" AND Restaurant.Hours = "7.30 a.m. - 4 p.m."
interpretation1: Show all buffets open between 7:30 am and 4:00pm, also show the coffee shops open during the same time.
interpretation2: Show all the buffets in the data, also show just the coffee shops open from 7:30am to 4:00pm.
